snippet.title: Amber Heard's Latest Plan of  Attack
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is reportedly going to London to testify against Johnny Depp in the Sun lawsuit trial.  She just might be shooting herself in the foot since testifying against Johnny Depp in court is breaking the NDA they both signed.  This has no bearing on the 7Mil she received from Johnny that she apparently donated to charity...that 7Mil was the legal settlement from the divorce since they did not have a prenup.  It was NOT a pay-off for her to stay silent despite what the Daily Mail article says about it.  Here is the article itself:

"Amber Heard will fly in to London next month to testify against ex-husband Johnny Depp over claims he beat her."
https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8060735/Amber-Heard-fly-London-month-testify-against-ex-husband-Johnny-Depp.html

It's obvious to me that Amber is trying to break Johnny Depp down by showing up at court to testify.  Johnny has been there in London testifying
on his own, and if she shows up they might share a courtroom together.  That won't be pleasant for Johnny but this is what narcissists like Amber plan well.  She is trying to make Johnny fall apart and crumble at her feet.  He's not going to do that at this point, as far as I can see, but it's  pretty clear that she's banking on it.  After all, he didn't want to bring her down in 2016, he wanted to settle out so they could both come away unscathed.  He loved that woman deeply.  However, a lot can happen in four years and we're now in 2020.
Johnny Depp, I have no doubt, will stand his ground and show that these text messages were mere rants to a friend and not actual threats.  Amber was the abuser and he was the victim, but  he's not a victim any more.  He's fighting back and not leaving any stone unturned.
